caption: (Translated by Google) Where are you? It’s so hard to find every time I come to Hawaii I want to eat taco and chicken gangjeong  (Original) 어디계시나요? 하와이 올때마다 찾기 너무 어려워요 타코랑 닭강정 먹고 싶어요

(Translated by Google) It was delicious!  No. 5 goblin trio  No. 8 Jumbo Chicken Taco  No. 13 Boneless Crispy Spicy Chicken  It fits the taste of the elderly too  It's right in front of Los, so you can eat after shopping?  Since it was on Route 72, the menu is on the beach.  It's perfect if you take it as a bento!  (Original) 넘 맛있었습니다!  5번 도깨비 트리오  8번 점보치킨타코  13번 뼈없는 크리스피 스파이시 치킨  어르신들도 입맛에 딱 맞습니다  로스 바로앞이라 쇼핑 후 식사하셔도 될 듯?  72번국도에 있었던 만큼 메뉴가 비치에  도시락으로 가져가서 드셔도 딱입니다!

(Translated by Google) Not long ago, it was famous for Sandy Beach restaurants! The menu price ranges from $ 8 to $ 20, and the affordable menu is evenly delicious.  The $ 20 goblin bitrio bowl (beef + chicken + shrimp) menu is really full and the amount of rice is so generous that it is full ..  All three menus I ordered had a salad. The combination of rice + meat + vegetables + nachos is perfect !! (I don't know exactly, but the menus are Hawaiian + Korean based on Mexican style)  In addition, the boss and the mother of the boss run together. The boss is really really so kind that I feel Korean's affection here !! There is a park in front of the food truck, so it's great to eat and go! Picnic feeling ~  (Original) 얼마 전까지 샌디비치 맛집으로 유명했던 곳! 메뉴 가격은 8~20달러이고, 저렴한 메뉴도 골고루 맛있다.  20달러짜리 도깨비트리오볼(비프+치킨+쉬림프) 메뉴 정말 알차고 밥 양도 넉넉해서 완전 배부름..  내가 시킨 세개의 메뉴에 모두 샐러드가 있었음.. 밥+고기+채소+나초의 조화가 완벽!! (정확하게는 모르겠지만 메뉴들이 멕시칸 스타일 기반으로 하와이안 + 코리안 느낌)  추가로 사장님과 사장님 어머님이 같이 운영하시는데 사장님 진짜로 정말로 너무 친절하셔서 한국인의 정을 여기서 느끼고 갑니다!! 푸드트럭 앞에 공원이 있어서 먹고 가기에도 참 좋아요! 피크닉 온 기분~

Very delicious, and the head man I charge knows how to make good humored jokes!! Very much recommend the boneless spicy chicken and the chicken skinless bowl!! My wife and I very much enjoyed the different flavored sides to go with the chicken.
